summary.Title: Nail technician

JobPositionInformation.Purpose:
nail technician

 

Florencenails i slagelse, Danmark søger kollega. hvis du er dygtig til at lave negle så er du velkommen til at kontakte os her på email: info@florencenails.dk.

vi har arbejdet mange år som negletenikker, vi har meget erfaring. vi har mange faste kunder. Elsker du kunst, vil du have et fast arbejde ? så tag kontakt til os hurtigst muligt.

 

Krav  : Du kan lide at arbejde som team Og er Møde stabil.

Du skal have erfaring med at lave negle eller vipper.

Du skal minimum kunne lave manicure eller pedicure, shellac.

Kontakt med os på e-mail : info@florencenails.dk

Adresse: Nygade 2 st th, 4200 Slagelse, Danmark.

 

 

Florencenails in slagelse, Denmark is looking for a colleague, if you are good at making nails then you are the one welcome to contact us here by email: info@florencenails.dk. we have worked for many years as nail technicians, we have a lot of experience. we have many regular customers. Do you love art, do you want a permanent job? so contact us as soon as possible.

 

Requirements: you like to work as a team You are meeting stable You got to have experience with making nails or eyelashes .

Minimum  is You can do manicure or pedicure, shellac Contact us on e-mail: info@florencenails.dk Address: Nygade 2 st th 4200 Slagelse, Denmark .
